  1737→
  1738→    // ── Indian Room leniency ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
  1739→    // Reduce strictness for casual slang that is not targeting another user.
  1740→    // Low-severity abuse gets 2 grace passes; medium gets 1 first-occurrence pass.
  1741→    // High/severe abuse, explicit, hate, threats, scams → always enforced.
  1742→    // Spam detection → always enforced.
